research/history/logs/agent_round_0191.stdout.log:4419:I inspected the implemented low-cost MoE-like families, costed them against the 1024x4096 proxy, and checked prior results. The highest-information next move is a param-only architecture swap into `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` on the existing small-K recipe: it stays at ~0.23x total cost, matches the current 'cheap shared coarse branch + expert residual cleanup' agenda, and specifically answers whether performance degrades more slowly at K=96 than the current small-K anchors.
research/history/logs/agent_round_0191.stdout.log:4424:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"shared_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式写成 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r)} Σ_{j∈S_e(r)} γ_{e,j}(r) c_{e,j}`，其中 `r = x - Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i`；`{u_i}` 是 shared coarse 静态向量库，`{c_{e,j}}` 是 expert residual 静态子库。它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表+加权求和，再做 expert residual 查表+选择性补偿”流水线，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。唯一主假设：相对 r188 仅切换到该 architecture，在保持 `K=96` 的 small-K low-cost recipe 下，显式把 shared/coarse branch 与 expert residual cleanup 分工开来，会比当前 small-K anchors 更慢地随 K 下降而退化，并在约 `0.23x total_cost` 内把 FVU 压到比现有 `K=96` 非 shared-routed probe 更低、且更接近 `<0.25x` 主前沿。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果这轮在约 0.23x 下接近或优于 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=96`，下一轮优先继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 以校准 shared/coarse 与 residual cleanup 的预算分配。","如果这轮仍明显落后于 `<0.25x` anchors，则可基本结束“cheap shared/coarse branch + routed residual cleanup”这条 trunk-free 低成本槽位，把预算转回别的 architecture-level probe。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地成本自检：`shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 在 `K=96, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下 selection≈0.13x、deployment≈0.09x、combined≈0.23x，显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","该 family 已有一次更高 K 证据：r183 在近同 low-cost recipe 的 `K=108` 上得到 `FVU≈0.1411`；本轮把问题收紧到 `K=96`，直接回答当前最重要的 small-K robustness。"],"reference_round":188,"self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r188 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。没有新增 tunable 参数，也没有代码落盘，因此不需要扩展到 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择这轮而不是继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk`/`lowrank_expert_topk` 扫 `K` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，是因为当前策略已明确要求优先做 architecture-level probe，并且这条 family 正好对应“先让 cheap shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的当前高优先级结构假设。主要风险是该 family 目前不在旧兼容表显式列名里，若运行时后处理仍按旧表过滤，需要后续补记忆层兼容登记；但从导出形式看它满足 LUTurbo 静态库有限加权和硬约束。","summary":"建议以 r188 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次落在 `<0.25x` 主战场内的 small-K matched architecture probe，用最低额外成本直接验证“shared coarse branch + expert residual cleanup”能否在 `K=96` 比现有 low-cost probes 更稳。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0153.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库 local top-k + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，所有库都为静态向量库、不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不得进入 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r152 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“全局 residual cleanup 是否足以支撑单 expert 激活路径”，从而把当前低成本最佳点从约 0.49x 进一步压到约 0.44x total_cost，同时尽量维持优于现有低成本前沿的 FVU。","summary":"建议以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。这不是继续细扫 `K` 轴，而是对当前最强低成本结构做一次更有结构信息的 matched-cost probe：验证 residual 补偿是否能让 `lowrank_expert_residual` 承受单 expert 路径，把总成本从约 0.49x 压到约 0.44x。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。之所以不继续顺着 `K` 做第三轮局部下压，是因为提示已明确要求不要让现有 family 的 K 轴邻域重新主导；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 比 `K=88` 更能回答一个新的结构问题：当前 lowrank+expert+residual 是否仍需要双 expert 才能工作。之所以值得做，是因为本轮不是把 `expert_topk` 上对单 expert 的负信号简单外推到这里，相反是利用 residual cleanup 做一次 matched-cost 复验；本地成本自检显示 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 会把总成本从 2064384 压到 1835008，约 0.49x→0.44x，信息增量明显大于继续小步压 K。主要风险是 quality 可能明显回退；若如此，也能更干净地确认当前 target 上这条 family 的低成本下限确实依赖双 expert 路由。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r152 已把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 推到 `<0.5x`：`K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 时 FVU=0.09837，当前低成本前沿最佳点已从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切换到该 family。","本地成本自检：在 r152 配方下改成 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 后，deployment_accesses=458752 不变、combined_accesses=1835008、combined_ratio≈0.44，明显左于 r152 的 2064384/0.49x，且低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是在已有有效结构上验证“单 expert + residual 是否可行”，不是把 `expert_topk` 的单 expert 负信号直接外推；它更接近当前提示要求的 matched-cost 结构性对照。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍能保持 FVU 接近或优于当前 `<0.5x` best=0.0984，则下一轮可继续只改 `K` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，把这条单 expert 路径进一步压向 0.4x 左右。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显失败，则可以更明确地记下：当前 target 上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本可用区仍依赖双 expert 路由，后续不应再在这条 family 上重复单 expert 试探。","如果该点形成新的非支配点但质量略退，则可把它作为更低成本 anchor，后续再决定是沿单 expert 分支继续压缩，还是回到新的 hetero-MoE family 做原型。"],"reference_round":152}
